was gonna get fired.

09:34.774 --> 09:37.376
- Bud, a lot of good's
gonna come from this.

09:37.443 --> 09:39.111
Kids will be safer in gym
because of you.

09:39.211 --> 09:41.414
- Let's just give--
let's just give the coach half.

09:41.480 --> 09:42.615
- Tom.

09:42.715 --> 09:43.883
You're a sweet guy.

09:43.950 --> 09:45.117
