09:49.455 --> 09:50.456
- I don't know, 7/8ths?

09:50.556 --> 09:52.258
- Wh--babe, that's even more!

09:52.325 --> 09:54.827
- Who even knows what these
numbers even mean anymore.

09:54.927 --> 09:56.429
I just don't want
the coach to suffer.

09:56.495 --> 09:58.297
