10:34.133 --> 10:36.168
Listen,
we have a surprise for you.

10:36.268 --> 10:37.803
- I think you've done enough,
okay?

10:37.870 --> 10:39.839
- I would love it if
you could just hear Tom out,

10:39.939 --> 10:41.841
because, uh,
he is about to perform

10:41.941 --> 10:43.476
a random act of generosity

10:43.542 --> 10:45.478
that is really gonna
touch your hearts.

